title: PML-N’s Hafeez ur Rehman wins NA-188 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) candidate, Hafeez ur Rehman Khan has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-188, Rajanpur-II by securing 85,936 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate, Sardar
Ahmad Ali Khan Dershak who bagged 70,206 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 50.5%.
